  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nOn run the compiler with `compilers.solc.docker: true` the docker containers are not automatically remove when it exits creating stoped containers pollution\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n`truffle compile`   -or-  `./node_modules/.bin/truffle compile`\r\n`docker container ls`\r\n\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nadding the --rm tag for automatically remove the container when it exits at: \r\n[https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/develop/packages/truffle-compile/compilerSupplier/loadingStrategies/Docker.js#L13](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/develop/packages/truffle-compile/compilerSupplier/loadingStrategies/Docker.js#L13)\r\n\r\nThe containers should be removed when exits\r\n\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nThe containers are not be removed when exits\r\n\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.0.29\r\n",
